data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Incredible opportunity in Peachtree City! This elegant garden style home on a corner lot is a rare gem in the Kedron Village and located in the top PTC school district!  You are greeted with 10'+ ceilings, hardwood floors, kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops throughout the home, a formal dining area and a cozy living room that's perfect for entertaining.  The primary suite features vaulted ceilings and a private en-suite with a large walk-in shower, two vanities, and plenty of storage space.  Walking distance to Kedron Elementary School, Kedron Aquatic Center, multiple country clubs and golf courses (Peachtree City is nationally recognized for golf cart paths)!!! Less than 2 miles away from local restaurants and retail shopping centers, a movie theater, Costco, Sam's club and easy access to interstate 85 for commuters.  PRIME location!
